            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Iudicio principali <expan><abbr>d<am>dd</am></abbr><ex>ominorum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n<am>nn</am></abbr><ex>ostrorum</ex></expan> Val<supplied reason="lost">e</supplied>ntiniani Valentis <lb n="2"/>et Gratiani &amp;lt;p=R&amp;gt;rincipum maximorum dispositione<surplus>m</surplus> <lb n="3"/>etiam inlustris viri utriusque militiae magistri E&amp;lt;q=O&amp;gt;ui<lb break="no" n="4"/>ti comitis Foscianus p<expan><ex>rae</ex><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ositus</ex></expan> legionis prim<supplied reason="lost">ae Mar</supplied>tiorum <lb n="5"/>una cum militibus sibi creditis h<supplied reason="lost">unc bur</supplied>gum a fun<lb break="no" n="6"/>damentis et construxit et ad <expan><abbr>sum</abbr><ex>m</ex></expan><supplied reason="lost">am man</supplied>um operis <lb n="7"/>consulatu<surplus>s</surplus> Gratiano Augus<supplied reason="lost">t</supplied>o bis e<supplied reason="lost">t Pr</supplied>obo viro cla<lb break="no" n="8"/>rissimo fecit pervenire 
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>In sechs Fragmente gebrochen. Reste von roter Farbe in den Buchstaben. (B): Soproni; Gróf - Gróh; AE 2000; Borhy: kleinere Leseabweichungen.</p>
            </div>
